daycare-1.jpg\",\"source\":\"static\",\"listingType\":\"free\"},{\"id\":\"ChIJ9ycO7o8zUYgRFBI3JhzRlzE\",\"name\":\"Blue Ridge Canine Academy\",\"businessType\":\"Indoor Dog Park\",\"description\":\"Blue Ridge Canine Academy has become the premier destination for Hickory dog owners. This facility features modern training facilities, experienced and certified staff, offering pet care. Their services creates a safe, climate-controlled environment. situated in a prime Hickory location. Reach out to Blue Ridge Canine Academy for a consultation\",\"slug\":\"blue-ridge-canine-academy\",\"address\":\"4725 16th St Dr NE\",\"street\":\"4725 16th St Dr NE\",\"city\":\"Hickory\",\"state\":\"NC\",\"zipCode\":\"28601\",\"full_address\":\"4725 16th St Dr NE, Hickory, NC 28601, USA\",\"latitude\":35.7963634,\"longitude\":-81.28644179999999,\"googlePlaceId\":\"ChIJ9ycO7o8zUYgRFBI3JhzRlzE\",\"phone\":\"(828) 514-8675\",\"website\":\"http://www.blueridgecanineacademy.com/\",\"rating\":5,\"reviewCount\":106,\"userRatingsTotal\":106,\"pricing\":{\"pricingSource\":\"unknown\",\"isFree\":false},\"placeTypes\":[\"point_of_interest\",\"establishment\"],\"dataQuality\":\"verified\",\"openingHours\":{\"Monday\":\"Closed\",\"Tuesday\":\"10:00 AM – 7:00 PM\",\"Wednesday\":\"10:00 AM – 7:00 PM\",\"Thursday\":\"10:00 AM – 7:00 PM\",\"Friday\":\"10:00 AM – 7:00 PM\",\"Saturday\":\"10:00 AM – 7:00 PM\",\"Sunday\":\"10:00 AM – 7:00 PM\"},\"faqs\":[],\"amenities\":{},\"photos\":[{\"url\":\"/images/parks/northcarolina/blue-ridge-canine-academy/blue-ridge-canine-academy-1.jpg\",\"type\":\"photo\",\"source\":\"website\"},{\"url\":\"/images/parks/northcarolina/blue-ridge-canine-academy/blue-ridge-canine-academy-2.jpg\",\"type\":\"photo\",\"source\":\"website\"}],\"photo\":\"/images/parks/northcarolina/blue-ridge-canine-academy/blue-ridge-canine-academy-1.jpg\",\"source\":\"static\",\"listingType\":\"free\"},{\"id\":\"ChIJz6Ot6Gs7UYgRaRN499T4WOc\",\"name\":\"Bruce Meisner Park\",\"businessType\":\"Indoor 